v3.0

* support to PDB files (input and output)
* incorporation of ensemble of conformations of molecule 2 (internal energies must be provided)
* added new loop over molecule 2 conformations
* updated filenames for coordinate files
* updated INPUT file strings
* updated script to run xtb calculations (utils/run_xtb)
* updated script to read xtb output files (utils/read_xtb)
* updated script to run path calculations (utils/run_path)
* updated script to convert gromacs topologies to themis parameters (utils/gmx2pdb)
* lib/libxdrfile.a recompiled
* add openmp parallelization for LJ+Coul potential
